## Backup & Recovery

<!-- {{#if tauri}} -->
### Desktop Backup

**Strategy**: User-managed backups

```rust
// Backup database to user-selected location
pub fn backup_database(dest_path: &str) -> Result<()> {
    let src = app_data_dir().join("data.db");
    std::fs::copy(src, dest_path)?;
    Ok(())
}
```

**Recommendations**:
- Export functionality in app
- Auto-backup on major updates
- Cloud sync option (if tauri-aws)
<!-- {{/if}} -->

<!-- {{#if nextjs-aws}} -->
### Cloud Backup

**Automated Backups**: RDS automatic backups

```typescript
// infrastructure/lib/db-stack.ts
backupRetention: Duration.days(7),
preferredBackupWindow: '03:00-04:00',  // UTC
deleteAutomatedBackups: false,
```

**Point-in-Time Recovery**: Enabled for 7 days

**Disaster Recovery**:
- RTO: < 4 hours
- RPO: < 5 minutes
